== Reception == Elliot Wagland from ''[[HuffPost|Huffington Post UK]]'' called the show "an enchanting way to spend an afternoon", saying that it "stunned" his son into silence.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2013/01/02/walking-with-dinosaurs-review_n_2396076.html|title=Walking With Dinosaurs (REVIEW): Prehistoric Monsters Roar Into The 02 In Spectacular Style|date=2013-01-02|work=HuffPost UK|access-date=2018-01-12|language=en-GB}}</ref>
